[Because of the rise in mumps outbreaks observed at US universities since 2006, a federal expert US panel has endorsed a 3rd vaccine dose in such outbreak situations. See http://wapo.st/2yoWDc1 for a report on this decision, as well as ProMED mail Mumps update (31): USA, MMR 3rd dose, Canada 20171027.5407525.

